Windows 10 is the newest version of the long running operating system created by Microsoft. In this book we will explore Windows 10 and many of its great features. You will learn why this program is so popular and how it can be used to perform a wide range of tasks we rely on day in and day out. At the end of this book you will have an amazing understanding of this software. In this book I will give you 33 great tips that are derived from observation and personal experience. Many of the tips and tricks that you will find will be very useful while others will relate to specific tasks for advanced users. No matter if you are a newbie or seasoned veteran there is something in this book for you.
